Crowdin,advanced,editor,helps,website,or,software,translators,to,work,faster,and,more,efficiently,The,Crowdin,API,provides,secure,programmatic,access,to,the,Crowdin,service,allowing,developers,to,build,tools,and,services,on,top,plus,Crowdin,can,integrate,with,development,processes,to,reach,continuous,localization,The,Crowdin,API,uses,a,RESTful,style,using,XML,over,HTTP,For,HTTP,requests,used,only,POST,method,Responses,are,formatted,in,XML,or,JSON